@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_ppzvrv(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(0.62)
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.cos((v0 + 0.21 + tmp + 0.84)))
    v2 = wp.sin((0.36 / (v0 + 0.87 + tmp + 0.20)))
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v1 + 0.11) / 0.42) - (wp.sin(v2 + 0.95) - (v0 + 0.64 + v2 + 0.34)))
    v0 = wp.exp(wp.cos((v1 + 0.65 * v1 + 0.26)))
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.abs(wp.abs(tmp + 0.15)))
    data[tid] = v0
